Class RabbitsGrassSimulationAgent

  • java.lang.Object
    • RabbitsGrassSimulationAgent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    uchicago.src.sim.gui.Drawable

    public class RabbitsGrassSimulationAgent
extends java.lang.Object
implements uchicago.src.sim.gui.Drawable
    Class that implements the simulation agent for the rabbits grass simulation. The rabbit agent includes basic internal variables, methods for modifying a rabbit's position and direction, ID variables, etc.
    Author:
    Swiss Federal Institute of Technology in Lausanne (EPFL), Switzerland
